CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, November 14, 1959, p. A3, reads: "Conerstone - Laying Team - This is the team of F. & A. M. Mason which took charge of cornerstone - laying ceremonies at Loendi Club, Sunday afternoon."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of Masons, possibly from 7th district, standing in semicircle around cornerstone inscribed 1959, with three glasses on top, for Loendi Club on Ledlie Street
